// Row 5 (QTY=0) would form its own group (ZZ9999/1) if it weren't excluded by the
// ->filter(r|$r.QTY>0) added to the positions() function body. Its exclusion is
// implicitly proven by groupBySuite's unchanged assertion still showing only the
// original two groups.
###Data
Data demo::relation::data::PositionData
{
  Relation
  #{
    default.PositionTable:
      ID,ACC_NUM,GSN,PRODUCT_ID,QTY
      1,7900002,YU2EF5,1,3
      2,7900002,YU2EF5,1,5
      3,7900003,EA4GNY,2,100
      4,7900003,EA4GNY,2,200
      5,7900005,ZZ9999,1,0;
  }#
}
